==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Black Spanish
<hw>Black Spanish</hw>. <def>One of an old and well-known Mediterranean
breed of domestic fowls with glossy black plumage, blue legs and feet,
bright red comb and wattles, and white face. They are remarkable as egg
layers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

